{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/posts/next-redux-wrapper","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"June"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"cc3e08b5-4d58-588f-a7ef-dec3f8125056","excerpt":"현재 Next.js와 함께 사용하는 skill set은 Redux (observable), Redux toolkit 입니다.\nSSR을 위해 Next.js를 사용하고 있는데, Custom server 코드가 아닌 Component 코드 만으로 최대한 data pre-fetching…","html":"<p>현재 Next.js와 함께 사용하는 skill set은 Redux (observable), Redux toolkit 입니다.\nSSR을 위해 Next.js를 사용하고 있는데, <a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/advanced-features/custom-server\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Custom server</a> 코드가 아닌 Component 코드 만으로 최대한 data pre-fetching을 하기 위해 <code class=\"language-text\">getInitialProps</code>를 사용합니다. (<a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/api-reference/data-fetching/getInitialProps\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">이젠 getServerSideProps, getStaticProps로 사용됨</a>)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Page</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> stars <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>Next stars<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>stars<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">getInitialProps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">ctx</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> res <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token function\">fetch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'https://api.github.com/repos/vercel/next.js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> json <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> res<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">json</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> stars<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> json<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>stargazers_count <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Page<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/43d9290520422c1f857d533b7b98f05a/536c7/default.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"default\"\n        title=\"default\"\n        src=\"/static/43d9290520422c1f857d533b7b98f05a/e85cb/default.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/43d9290520422c1f857d533b7b98f05a/070ae/default.png 120w,\n/static/43d9290520422c1f857d533b7b98f05a/8ff5a/default.png 240w,\n/static/43d9290520422c1f857d533b7b98f05a/e85cb/default.png 480w,\n/static/43d9290520422c1f857d533b7b98f05a/37523/default.png 720w,\n/static/43d9290520422c1f857d533b7b98f05a/d9199/default.png 960w,\n/static/43d9290520422c1f857d533b7b98f05a/536c7/default.png 1480w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이 때, redux를 사용 중이고, <code class=\"language-text\">getInitialProps</code>에서 <code class=\"language-text\">dispatch</code>를 사용해 store를 업데이트를 하려면 어떻게 해야 할까요?</p>\n<h2 id=\"간단한-해결책은-next-redux-wrapper-라이브러리를-사용하는-것입니다\" style=\"position:relative;\">간단한 해결책은 <a href=\"https://github.com/kirill-konshin/next-redux-wrapper\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><code class=\"language-text\">next-redux-wrapper</code></a> 라이브러리를 사용하는 것입니다.<a href=\"#%EA%B0%84%EB%8B%A8%ED%95%9C-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0%EC%B1%85%EC%9D%80-next-redux-wrapper-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EA%B2%83%EC%9E%85%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"간단한 해결책은 next redux wrapper 라이브러리를 사용하는 것입니다 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers-- after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>redux configure에 대한 약간의 설정은 필요하지만, 번거로운 작업 없이 getInitialProps에서 fetch한 데이터를 server side의 store에 저장한 뒤, 이를 client side의 store로 그대로 넘길 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/821263d3022cd15658c28fa8da0ad3b3/3ceac/next-redux-wrapper.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"next-redux-wrapper\"\n        title=\"next-redux-wrapper\"\n        src=\"/static/821263d3022cd15658c28fa8da0ad3b3/e85cb/next-redux-wrapper.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/821263d3022cd15658c28fa8da0ad3b3/070ae/next-redux-wrapper.png 120w,\n/static/821263d3022cd15658c28fa8da0ad3b3/8ff5a/next-redux-wrapper.png 240w,\n/static/821263d3022cd15658c28fa8da0ad3b3/e85cb/next-redux-wrapper.png 480w,\n/static/821263d3022cd15658c28fa8da0ad3b3/37523/next-redux-wrapper.png 720w,\n/static/821263d3022cd15658c28fa8da0ad3b3/d9199/next-redux-wrapper.png 960w,\n/static/821263d3022cd15658c28fa8da0ad3b3/3ceac/next-redux-wrapper.png 1456w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>하지만 문제는, 사용하려고 했던 스펙 중 <code class=\"language-text\">Redux-observable</code>에 대한 support가 이루어지지 않는 부분이었습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4926ce354edb31d89a0315b840a1cad1/442cb/supports.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.83333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"supports\"\n        title=\"supports\"\n        src=\"/static/4926ce354edb31d89a0315b840a1cad1/e85cb/supports.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4926ce354edb31d89a0315b840a1cad1/070ae/supports.png 120w,\n/static/4926ce354edb31d89a0315b840a1cad1/8ff5a/supports.png 240w,\n/static/4926ce354edb31d89a0315b840a1cad1/e85cb/supports.png 480w,\n/static/4926ce354edb31d89a0315b840a1cad1/37523/supports.png 720w,\n/static/4926ce354edb31d89a0315b840a1cad1/442cb/supports.png 752w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>support 항목엔 없었지만, <a href=\"https://github.com/kirill-konshin/next-redux-wrapper/issues/303\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">아래 issue의 답변</a>처럼 observable에서도 사용 가능하다는 뉘앙스를 확인할 수 있었습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a9396690eda163a1810a9f3443dc47be/7e318/observable-supports.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 16.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAf0lEQVQI13WLaw6DIBAGuf/12t5AQLS8YqAKwldYif3VTSazmeyy1+OJaeIwzkOtb1i/3YS4I50FRz6xH7mRhn/7Z09067dAjS3LCuccVDMXkpi4IIScIWdFzRgLYx1ZN5z37c9Da3N1a5FSBsOYGCMRQhiOd+uUUlBr/Uuf7i/B4ObZCwWZegAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"observable-supports\"\n        title=\"observable-supports\"\n        src=\"/static/a9396690eda163a1810a9f3443dc47be/e85cb/observable-supports.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a9396690eda163a1810a9f3443dc47be/070ae/observable-supports.png 120w,\n/static/a9396690eda163a1810a9f3443dc47be/8ff5a/observable-supports.png 240w,\n/static/a9396690eda163a1810a9f3443dc47be/e85cb/observable-supports.png 480w,\n/static/a9396690eda163a1810a9f3443dc47be/37523/observable-supports.png 720w,\n/static/a9396690eda163a1810a9f3443dc47be/d9199/observable-supports.png 960w,\n/static/a9396690eda163a1810a9f3443dc47be/7e318/observable-supports.png 1892w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>redux-saga와 redux-observable로 PoC를 구성하여 기술적 테스트를 진행하였는데, redux-saga에선 아래와 같이 정상적인 동작이 나왔습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8201661ba75a3322ad1487bb533cb14a/75a80/redux-saga-normal.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 235.83333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"redux-saga-normal\"\n        title=\"redux-saga-normal\"\n        src=\"/static/8201661ba75a3322ad1487bb533cb14a/e85cb/redux-saga-normal.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8201661ba75a3322ad1487bb533cb14a/070ae/redux-saga-normal.png 120w,\n/static/8201661ba75a3322ad1487bb533cb14a/8ff5a/redux-saga-normal.png 240w,\n/static/8201661ba75a3322ad1487bb533cb14a/e85cb/redux-saga-normal.png 480w,\n/static/8201661ba75a3322ad1487bb533cb14a/37523/redux-saga-normal.png 720w,\n/static/8201661ba75a3322ad1487bb533cb14a/d9199/redux-saga-normal.png 960w,\n/static/8201661ba75a3322ad1487bb533cb14a/75a80/redux-saga-normal.png 1134w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">2. Page.getStaticProps uses the store to dispatch things</code>가 getInitialProps에서 data fetch하는 action을 실행한 로그입니다. (이후 내부에서 비동기로 update action이 실행 됨) 이후 <code class=\"language-text\">3. getProps after dispatches has store state</code> 로그에서 데이터가 제대로 업데이트 된 모습을 볼 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8683332316adcf6599d84f062e0939b1/f73a1/redux-observable-issue.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 210%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"redux-observable-issue\"\n        title=\"redux-observable-issue\"\n        src=\"/static/8683332316adcf6599d84f062e0939b1/e85cb/redux-observable-issue.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8683332316adcf6599d84f062e0939b1/070ae/redux-observable-issue.png 120w,\n/static/8683332316adcf6599d84f062e0939b1/8ff5a/redux-observable-issue.png 240w,\n/static/8683332316adcf6599d84f062e0939b1/e85cb/redux-observable-issue.png 480w,\n/static/8683332316adcf6599d84f062e0939b1/37523/redux-observable-issue.png 720w,\n/static/8683332316adcf6599d84f062e0939b1/f73a1/redux-observable-issue.png 822w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>하지만 observable에선 <code class=\"language-text\">2. Page.getStaticProps uses the store to dispatch things</code>로그가 나오는 getInitialProps에서 data fetch를 하였으나, <code class=\"language-text\">3. getProps after dispatches has store state</code> 로그에서 데이터가 제대로 들어오지 않은 모습을 볼 수 있습니다. 현재 이미지에는 없으나, Server에서 Client로 store를 넘겨주는 <code class=\"language-text\">__NEXT_REDUX_WRAPPER_HYDRATE__</code> 로그 단계 이후에 Server측 store의 data가 업데이트 되는 로그가 나왔습니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>saga와 observable의 차이는 아래와 같이 rootStore를 구성할 때, 3번 영역처럼 sagaTask를 가진다는점 이었습니다.\n하지만 이는 redux-saga자체에서 지원하는 기능으로, redux-observable에선 .run 실행 시, return type이 void 입니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// store.tsx</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SagaStore</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Store</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    sagaTask<span class=\"token operator\">?</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Task<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> makeStore<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> MakeStore<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>State<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">context<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Context</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 1: Create the middleware</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> sagaMiddleware <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">createSagaMiddleware</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 2: Add an extra parameter for applying middleware:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> store <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">createStore</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>reducer<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">applyMiddleware</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>sagaMiddleware<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 3: Run your sagas on server</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>store <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> SagaStore<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sagaTask <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> sagaMiddleware<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>rootSaga<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 4: now return the store:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> store<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ------------------------------------------------------------------</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// pages/index.tsx</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> getServerSideProps <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ReduxWrapper<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getServerSideProps</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> store<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> req<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> res<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>etc <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// regular stuff</span>\n    store<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dispatch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ApplicationSlice<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>actions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">updateConfiguration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// end the saga</span>\n    store<span class=\"token punctuation\">.<